name.family:
#1 @ 9 yrs - 5 days, male, Cervarix 
Evaluation_Test_Type: Inadvertent vaccine
General_Description: This test case describes when a vaccine dose is given less than the vaccine grace period and that vaccine (Cervarix)  is administered to a male that the dose is not valid and that a subsequent dose of a preferred or allowed vaccine should be administered as soon as possible.
